        <text>
          <![CDATA[ <p><strong>Global Magnitsky Human Rights Accountability Extension Act</strong></p> <p>This bill extends through December 31, 2034, the authority of the President to impose sanctions on foreign persons involved in certain gross violations of internationally recognized human rights and significant acts of corruption. </p>]]>
        </text>
